      <scopecontent id="aspace_89c95925ebab74c39b1bce5c5b457eae">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of memorabilia, photographs, artifacts, and an engraving documenting Franklin Lindley Couch's (Yale 1917) extracurricular activities while a student at Yale. Included are materials documenting the Yale Courant staff, Beta Theta Pi fraternity, Calcium Light Night, and the Yale Field Artillery in World War I.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
